    "body": "So I meant to close that one down :-)\n\nWe can't really do that autoconf-like, unless we want to install a system-wide header that has been generated based on that detection. I still believe such thing is an abomination - a system header that mutates per-installation that is. The approach I took on #1185 was to add this:\n\nhttps://github.com/grpc/grpc/blob/master/include/grpc%2B%2B/config.h#L44\n"
